Package org.mule.extension.fix.api

Class FIXMessage

java.lang.Object
org.mule.extension.fix.api.FIXMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class FIXMessage extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a FIX Protocol message with proper field ordering and checksum calculation. FIX messages use tag=value pairs separated by SOH (Start of Header, ASCII 0x01).
